{"data":[{"id":562989124,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2803f9cecfbed22c5886b4657ecea19f","url_token":"xi-xi-cheng-jue-21-91","name":"夕夕成玦","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2803f9cecfbed22c5886b4657ecea19f","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562989124","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546169788,"updated_time":1546224582,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":11,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e答主的逻辑是表达\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e该高中生的水平＜＜集训队保送＜imo金牌＜＜＜＜（答主发明的远远远远小于）陈景润\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，该高中生已经完全否定了我这个逻辑，毕竟他的证明没用什么知识。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能我是嫉妒天才，但是如果我嫉妒的真是天才，又有什么所谓呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e毕竟这个level的天才世人都会嫉妒的吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e－－－－－－－\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数竞党在自己的角度认真地回答问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学竞赛的体系是这样的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先是省一级预赛，各省自己出题自己组织。题目一般比高考数学略难，是的也就是比错位相减洛必达法则略难。当然了预赛一般没什么用，重要的是后面的比赛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后就是高联了，全名全国高中数学联赛。跟高考数学有可比性的就是一试了吧，一试和高考数学中间隔了一个自招档，也就是说高联一试一般比高考高两个档。按我自己的感受，一个档的意思就是本档的优秀生大概能做到上一档的中档题吧。但注意这只是一试，在高联满分300分中占120分。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e剩下的180分叫二试或者加试。一共四道题，其中有一个类型叫做数论。既然您能证出哥德巴赫猜想想必很了解数论了。这部分的难度就不和高考比较了，毕竟已经不是一个体系。如果您能够做出三道并且一试90分以上，您可以进入省代表队，也就是说您比包括我在内的绝大多数学了1年至5年不等的数学竞赛的所谓竞赛生走的要远了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之后的考试我就无法亲身接触了，所以略谈一下。省队队员可以进入冬令营，也就是中国数学奥林匹克（CMO），在其中的300余人中，前60名可以到达您的要求也就是保送清北。而这60名集训队队员会经过预备队国家队两次选拔进入国家队。成为代表中国参加imo的6人之一。像您这么优秀肯定能代表中国取得满分金牌。此时您离哥德巴赫猜想的距离有多远呢我也不知道。但据我对您的观感您可能离这一步还有一些距离吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不用证明哥猜，您先拿个满分金牌，那样至少你可能能进北大数院的教学楼了。然后可以将您的五页\u003ci\u003e长篇\u003c/i\u003e论文面呈教授，多好。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"答主的逻辑是表达该高中生的水平＜＜集训队保送＜imo金牌＜＜＜＜（答主发明的远远远远小于）陈景润当然了，该高中生已经完全否定了我这个逻辑，毕竟他的证明没用什么知识。可能我是嫉妒天才，但是如果我嫉妒的真是天才，又有什么所谓呢。毕竟这个level的天…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=210\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%